## 10. Data partitioning

См. § 2 для **когда** добавлять. Здесь — **как**.

### 10.1. Стратегии partitioning

| Стратегия | Когда |
|---|---|
| **Range partitioning** (по дате) | Time-series data, logs, events. Partition pruning при дате-range queries. |
| **List partitioning** (по value) | Discrete values (region, tenant_id). Если values известны upfront. |
| **Hash partitioning** | Even distribution когда нет natural range / list. |

### 10.2. PostgreSQL declarative partitioning

```sql
CREATE TABLE events (
  id bigserial,
  occurred_at timestamptz NOT NULL,
  ...
) PARTITION BY RANGE (occurred_at);

CREATE TABLE events_2026_05 PARTITION OF events
  FOR VALUES FROM ('2026-05-01') TO ('2026-06-01');
```

Автоматическое creation new partitions: `pg_partman` extension.

### 10.3. Partition pruning

Queries должны filter по partition key чтобы planner мог skip irrelevant partitions:

```sql
-- ✅ Pruning works (filter on partition key)
SELECT * FROM events WHERE occurred_at > '2026-05-01';

-- ❌ No pruning (no filter on partition key)
SELECT * FROM events WHERE user_id = 123;
```

Indexes per partition, не cross-partition.

### 10.4. Drop old partitions

Часто benefit partitioning — `ALTER TABLE DROP PARTITION` instead of `DELETE FROM`. Instant cleanup без VACUUM cost.

