## 11. Multi-tenancy isolation

См. § 2 для **когда** добавлять. Здесь — **как**.

### 11.1. Стратегии

| Стратегия | Когда | Tradeoffs |
|---|---|---|
| **App-level + tenant_id column** | Default для большинства SaaS | + Simple, single schema migration. − Bugs в WHERE могут cross-tenant leak. |
| **Row-level security (RLS)** | Hardening против app bugs | + DB enforces isolation. − Complexity, debug headache. |
| **Schema-per-tenant** | Strict isolation + tenants < thousands | + True isolation. − Migrations × N tenants, connection pool per schema. |
| **Database-per-tenant** | Compliance / per-customer custom | + Strongest isolation. − Operational overhead, cost. |

### 11.2. PostgreSQL RLS

```sql
ALTER TABLE invoices ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;

CREATE POLICY tenant_isolation ON invoices
  USING (tenant_id = current_setting('app.current_tenant_id')::bigint);
```

App sets `SET LOCAL app.current_tenant_id = '<tenant>'` per request. RLS auto-filters.

### 11.3. Cross-tenant operations

Admin endpoints / cross-tenant analytics — explicit bypass:

```sql
-- Admin role bypasses RLS
GRANT BYPASSRLS ON SCHEMA public TO admin_role;
```

Документируем где bypass используется + audit log every cross-tenant query.

