## 14. Backups + restore drills

**Этот раздел — самый часто игнорируемый и самый дорогой при провале.**

### 14.1. RTO / RPO — определены upfront

- **RTO** (Recovery Time Objective) — за сколько мы должны восстановить работу после failure
- **RPO** (Recovery Point Objective) — сколько данных можем потерять (час? минута? ноль?)

| Product type | Typical RTO | Typical RPO |
|---|---|---|
| Hobby / experimental | 24 hours | 24 hours |
| Small SaaS | 4 hours | 1 hour |
| Production SaaS | 1 hour | 15 minutes |
| Financial / health | 15 min | < 1 minute |

RPO determines backup frequency: RPO 1 hour = WAL archive every hour (или continuous streaming).

### 14.2. Backup стратегии

| Стратегия | Когда |
|---|---|
| **Full dump** ежедневно | RPO < 1 day, простой recovery model |
| **Full weekly + incremental daily** | Storage cost / time tradeoff |
| **WAL archiving + base backup** (PITR) | RPO минуты, point-in-time recovery |
| **Streaming replication + delayed replica** | Hot standby + protection от accidental drop |
| **Continuous backup** (managed services) | Stripe / cloud-provider managed |

### 14.3. Storage discipline

- **3-2-1 rule:** 3 copies, 2 different media, 1 off-site
- **Encryption at rest** для backups (см. § 9.3)
- **Retention policy:**
  - Daily для 7 days
  - Weekly для 4 weeks
  - Monthly для 12 months
  - Yearly для regulatory retention period
- **Verification** что backup readable (NOT just «backup file exists»)

### 14.4. Off-site copies

- Different region / different cloud provider
- Не same datacenter / не same blast radius
- Encrypted in transit + at rest

### 14.5. Restore drills — **обязательны**

«Untested backup = no backup.» Restore drill regularly:

- **Production-tier:** monthly restore to staging from prod backup, verify schema + sample data
- **Disaster recovery drill:** quarterly — restore entire system in alternate region / cloud, measure RTO
- **Documentation:** runbook для restore в `incident-runbook-draft.md` (см. AP-13)

Метрика: «когда последний раз делали restore drill» — quarterly maximum gap.

### 14.6. Backup access control

- Restricted IAM роль (не shared с app)
- MFA для restore operations
- Audit log restore attempts

### 14.7. Pre-incident readiness

В `incident-runbook-draft.md`:

- Команды для restore (parameterized, ready-to-run)
- Contact list (whose to wake up)
- Communication template для users / status page
- Post-mortem template

